OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1776723068
OL,3,CSister of disgraced surgeon's patient
OL,4,Cdemands her scars be shown in court
OL,6,FThe sister of a serving West Midlands
OL,7,FPolice officer has demanded that
OL,8,Fimages of her body be shown during the
OL,9,Finquest into her death, to show the
OL,10,Falleged malpractice of her breast
OL,11,Fsurgeon.
OL,13,FMarie Pinfield was 47 when she was
OL,14,Fdiagnosed with breast cancer in 2006.
OL,15,FShe died in 2008.
OL,17,FShe is one of 69 women whose deaths
OL,18,Fare being investigated by a coroner
OL,19,Fover concerns they may have been
OL,20,Funnatural, as a result of the actions
OL,21,Fof their breast surgeon, Ian Paterson.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1776723068
OL,3,CSister of disgraced surgeon's patient
OL,4,Cdemands her scars be shown in court
OL,6,FGiving evidence in the hearing, which
OL,7,Fhas been delayed by 13 months, in
OL,8,FBirmingham on Monday, Marie's sister,
OL,9,FShirley Moroney, told the court her
OL,10,Fsister had explicitly asked Paterson
OL,11,Fto remove her breasts because she was
OL,12,Fconcerned about the cancer returning.
OL,14,FShe explained to the court how, before
OL,15,FMarie's surgery, she was shown images
OL,16,Fof women who had undergone the same
OL,17,Foperation by breast care nurses at
OL,18,FSolihull Hospital.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1776723068
OL,3,CSister of disgraced surgeon's patient
OL,4,Cdemands her scars be shown in court
OL,6,F"We were told to prepare ourselves
OL,7,Fbecause we were going to see images of
OL,8,Fa woman without breasts," Shirley said.
OL,10,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,11,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,12,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,13,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,15,F"We talked about it after and felt it
OL,16,Fwas a bit overdramatic. We went into
OL,17,Fthe pamphlet, and she said, 'That's
OL,18,Fit, that's what I want'."
OL,26,@nD@AOUzD@YO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
