CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1776723068
OL,3,CSister of disgraced surgeon's patient
OL,4,Cdemands her scars be shown in court
OL,6,FShirley told the court that when her
OL,7,Fsister came out of the operation, she
OL,8,Fthought that they had decided not to
OL,9,Ftake away her breasts at all.
OL,11,F"Even though she was in a lying down
OL,12,Fposition, I could still see quite a
OL,13,Flot of volume on her body," she said.
OL,15,FMarie later complained to Paterson
OL,16,Fabout that operation, and she was
OL,17,Fscheduled for further surgery another
OL,18,Fmonth later, in October 2006.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1776723068
OL,3,CSister of disgraced surgeon's patient
OL,4,Cdemands her scars be shown in court
OL,6,FShirley explained that after two
OL,7,Fmastectomies, her sister still did not
OL,8,Fhave a flat chest wall.
OL,10,FThe inquest then heard how Marie was
OL,11,Fseen by another breast surgeon, Hemant
OL,12,FIngle, in 2007, who ordered some
OL,13,Fphotographs to be taken of Marie's
OL,14,Fbody as he had concerns about the
OL,15,Fsurgery that had been undertaken.
OL,17,FCounsel to the Inquest told the court
OL,18,Fthat she was not going to show the
OL,19,Fimages of Marie's body in the
OL,20,Fcourtroom.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30306
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1776723068
OL,3,CSister of disgraced surgeon's patient
OL,4,Cdemands her scars be shown in court
OL,6,FShirley said, "I'd like you to show
OL,7,Fthem."
OL,9,FPaterson, who is attending the inquest
OL,10,Fonline from prison where he is serving
OL,11,Fa 20-year prison sentence for wounding
OL,12,Fpatients in the private sector, was
OL,13,Fonline watching the hearing in the
OL,14,Fminutes leading up to the moment the
OL,15,Fphotographs were shown.
OL,17,FThere was silence in the courtroom as
OL,18,Fthe screen scrolled through the five
OL,19,Fimages of Marie's body and scars,
OL,20,Fwhich were taken by a medical
OL,21,Fphotographer on July 31 2007.
OL,26,@nD@OOUoD@FO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30307
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1776723068
OL,3,CSister of disgraced surgeon's patient
OL,4,Cdemands her scars be shown in court
OL,6,FAt the start of the hearing, Shirley
OL,7,Fhad been reluctant to begin her
OL,8,Fevidence until Paterson appeared on
OL,9,Fthe video link.
OL,11,FThe coroner told the court that while
OL,12,FPaterson is compelled to give evidence
OL,13,Fin these hearings about his work, he
OL,14,Fis not required to listen to the
OL,15,Fevidence of others.
OL,17,FHis Honour Richard Foster, who is
OL,18,Fleading the investigations, said: "Mr
OL,19,FPaterson is not online but has a right
OL,20,Fnot to attend.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30308
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1776723068
OL,3,CSister of disgraced surgeon's patient
OL,4,Cdemands her scars be shown in court
OL,6,F"A facility is set up at the prison,
OL,7,Fand he has a facility to attend if he
OL,8,Fwants to. The only power I have is to
OL,9,Fmake him give evidence. And he is
OL,10,Fgiving evidence when required to do so.
OL,12,F"All I can say is the proceedings are
OL,13,Fbeing recorded and transcribed. I
OL,14,Fcan't make him attend, for that I
OL,15,Fapologise."
OL,17,FShirley began with a photograph of
OL,18,FMarie in uniform, shown on the screen,
OL,19,Fand another photograph in a frame sat
OL,20,Fon the desk next to her.
OL,26,@wD@KO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
