PN,30309
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1776723068
OL,3,CSister of disgraced surgeon's patient
OL,4,Cdemands her scars be shown in court
OL,6,FShe told the court: "Some people say
OL,7,Fthat their loved ones lit up a room.
OL,8,FMarie set it on fire. "
OL,10,FGiving evidence on Monday, Paterson
OL,11,Ftold the inquest hearing: "I don't
OL,12,Frecall Marie, I can't see Marie's
OL,13,Fface. I recall her case because there
OL,14,Fwas a lot of noise around. And she
OL,15,Fhad, quite simply, the largest breasts
OL,16,FI've ever operated on."
OL,18,FSo far, 68 inquests have been opened
OL,19,Finto the deaths of patients of the
OL,20,Fjailed breast surgeon.
OL,26,@pD@WOUxD@WO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/13
