PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1776723068
OL,3,CSister of disgraced surgeon's patient
OL,4,Cdemands her scars be shown in court
OL,6,FOne inquest has been concluded, and HM
OL,7,FCoroner has heard evidence in 29
OL,8,Finquests.
OL,10,FThere are 38 outstanding inquests,
OL,11,Fwhere families are still waiting for
OL,12,Fthe details of the care their loved
OL,13,Fones received to be examined by the
OL,14,Fcourt.
OL,16,FOn Tuesday, a 69th inquest is opening
OL,17,Finto the death of Karen Stone, another
OL,18,Fpatient who was treated by Paterson.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
