PN,30311
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1776723068
OL,3,CSister of disgraced surgeon's patient
OL,4,Cdemands her scars be shown in court
OL,6,FITV News previously reported how the
OL,7,Finvestigation is expected to cost #6.5
OL,8,Fmillion.
OL,10,FPaterson was found guilty of 17 counts
OL,11,Fof wounding patients with intent,
OL,12,Fagainst ten victims, at Nottingham
OL,13,FCrown Court in 2017.
OL,15,FHe was initially handed a 15-year
OL,16,Fprison term, but in 2018, Court of
OL,17,FAppeal judges increased his tariff to
OL,18,F20 years.
OL,20,FThese inquests are now the fifth
OL,21,Finvestigation into his practices.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
