FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30312
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1776723068
OL,3,CSister of disgraced surgeon's patient
OL,4,Cdemands her scars be shown in court
OL,6,FIn 2020, there was an inquiry which
OL,7,Fheard Paterson had been carrying out
OL,8,Fan unapproved version of a mastectomy,
OL,9,Fleaving some breast tissue behind.
OL,11,FPaterson is due for release from
OL,12,Fprison in May 2027, likely before the
OL,13,Ffirst phase of the inquests is
OL,14,Fcompleted.
OL,16,FA campaign against his release while
OL,17,Fthe coronial investigation continues
OL,18,Fhas received 29,000 signatures online.
OL,20,FPaterson has always denied any
OL,21,Fwrongdoing.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/13
